Title: Comment on covariant Stora--Zumino chain terms

Comments: Latex file, no figures

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B455 (1999) 197-199

In a recent paper, Ekstrand proposed a simple expression from which covariantanomaly, covariant Schwinger term and higher covariant chain terms may becomputed. We comment on the relation of his result to the earlier work ofTsutsui.